title: Oracle 26ai Vector Search Process Flow

direction: right

UserQuery: {
  label: User Query
  style: {
    fill: "#dcfce7"
    stroke: "#22c55e"
  }
}

TextEmbedding: {
  label: Text Embedding
  style: {
    fill: "#fef3c7"
    stroke: "#f59e0b"
  }
}

VectorRepresentation: {
  label: Vector Representation
  style: {
    fill: "#e0e7ff"
    stroke: "#6366f1"
  }
}

VectorDatabaseIndex: {
  label: Vector Database Index
  shape: cylinder
  style: {
    fill: "#d1d5db"
    stroke: "#374151"
  }
}

SimilarityCalculation: {
  label: Similarity Calculation
  style: {
    fill: "#fce7f3"
    stroke: "#ec4899"
  }
}

RankedResults: {
  label: Ranked Results
  style: {
    fill: "#dbeafe"
    stroke: "#0284c7"
  }
}

UserQuery -> TextEmbedding: Convert to vector
TextEmbedding -> VectorRepresentation: Generate embeddings
VectorRepresentation -> VectorDatabaseIndex: Search index
VectorDatabaseIndex -> SimilarityCalculation: Find similar vectors
SimilarityCalculation -> RankedResults: Return top matches
